com.sri.ai.expresso.api

Interface Parser

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AntlrGrinderParserWrapper

    @Beta
public interface Parser
    A parser maps strings to the corresponding Expressions. To give implementations a chance to free up resources and save caches, the interface requires the method close() to be called before finishing the application.
